ndnan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/legendnan","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6eef091e644dcb3433da7f8b490ed27d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":729776,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1606054961","description":"<p>这是我两年前买的，现在要是处新版我绝对不会买了，另外，这个 monitor 有办法关吗？能关的话就不卸了，粉碎机还蛮好用的</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/0081Kckwgy1gl3ju7exepj30f20h8tb7.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>这会占用 90%了，截图的时候才 68%</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/729776","replies":69,"created_ts":1606446210,"created":"11:03:30","title":"大家别买 cleanmymac，流氓","author":"GTD","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/GTD","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f94c/109c/481920_mini.png?m=1597921718"},{"id":729909,"node":"PostgreSQL","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/postgresql","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9be4/0cee/365_mini.png?m=1524176193","description":"<p>说到关系型数据库，很多人就会说 MySQL 。其实严格来讲，MySQL 5.6 以前都不像一个严谨的关系型数据库，5.7 、8.0 之后虽有改观，但相比 PostgreSQL 、Oracle 、SQLServer 其实还有距离。</p>\n<p>当然现实情况是，国內大家都比较熟悉 MySQL，虽然 DBEngine 上的排名显示 PostgreSQL 与 MySQL 的比例已经从前两年的 1:5 到了现在的 1:2.x 。</p>\n<p>这里就想做个简单的调研，有多少人知道或者用过 PostgreSQL ？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/729909","replies":52,"created_ts":1606464381,"created":"16:06:21","title":"就想问问多少人知道 PostgreSQL ？","author":"dhysum","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dhysum","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e523/eebf/18837_mini.png?m=1338270384"},{"id":729981,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1606054938","description":"<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.sketchapp.com/uploads/speed-graph-1@2x.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpo